  <brief_title>Research of Zoledronic Acid and Aromatase Inhibitors as Adjuvant Therapy to Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>esozao</acronym>
  <official_title>The Effectiveness and Safety of Treating Operable Breast Cancer by the Adjuvant Therapy of Zoledronic Acid and Aromatase Inhibitors and/or Ovarian Function Inhibition</official_title>
